description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of New York finale, which featured a new Lu song, drag queen bingo, and Dorinda unhinged. Bravo also released the Real Housewives of Orange County trailer, and part 1 of the Real Housewives of Beverly Hills reunion.


RHOBH Reunion: 29:36ish


YOUTUBE: YouTube.com/DannyPellegrino1
